<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
 <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Audiowide&family=Orbitron:wght@400..900&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png">
  <title>Login</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background-image: url(/loginBG.gif);
      background-size: cover;

      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-evenly;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Audiowide", sans-serif;
      flex-direction: column;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Audiowide", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: normal;
      margin-left: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .stack {
      position: relative;
      width: 320px;
      height: 400px;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .sheet {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 2px solid gold;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px gold;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      animation: glow 2s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    .sheet:nth-child(2) {
      transform: translate(10px, 10px);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .sheet:nth-child(3) {
      transform: translate(20px, 20px);
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .login-form {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      padding: 30px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .login-form h2 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
    }

    .login-form input {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 2px solid gold;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px gold;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: black;
      color: gold;
    }

    .login-form input[type="submit"] {
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: black;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 2px solid gold;
      color: gold;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .login-form input[type="submit"]:hover {
      background: gold;
      color: black;
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      0%, 100% {
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px gold;
      }
      50% {
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px gold;
      }
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.02);
      }
    }

    .pillar-left{
        position: absolute;
        left: 20vw;
        height: 100%;
        width: 50px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap:24px;
         animation: scroll-up 10s linear infinite;
         font-family: "Rajdhani", sans-serif;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    .pillar-left p{
        transform: rotate(-90deg);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
    }
    .pillar-right{
        position: absolute;
        right: 20vw;
        height: 100%;
        width: 50px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap:50px;
         animation: scroll-up 10s linear infinite;
         font-family: "Orbitron", sans-serif;
        font-optical-sizing: auto;
        font-weight: bold;
       font-style: normal;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    
    .pillar-right p{
        transform: rotate(90deg);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
      text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
    }
    @keyframes scroll-up {
   0%   { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%  { transform: translateY(-50%); }
  100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  
   .login-form p{
     color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
     text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
    }
   
   p a{
    color: rgb(243, 255, 71);
    text-shadow:
        0 0 5px gold,
        0 0 15px orange,
        0 0 25px white;
   }
   input{
  font-family: "Audiowide", sans-serif;
   }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
   
  <h1>CORTUANT</h1>

  <div class="stack">
    <div class="sheet"></div>
    <div class="sheet"></div>
    <div class="sheet login-form">
      <h2>Login</h2>
       <form action="/login" method="POST">
         <input type="text" placeholder="Username" name="username" />
         <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password"/>
         <input type="submit" value="Log in"></button>
       </form>
      <p><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>&nbsp;instead ?</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  
  <div class="pillar-left">  
        <p>फ़ाइल</p><p> अपलोड</p><p>केंद्र</p><p>|</p><p>डेटा</p><p>स्थानांतरण</p>
      <p>सक्रिय</p><p>|</p><p>100%</p><p>सुरक्षा</p><p>|</p>
  </div>

  
  <div class="pillar-right">
      <p>ЦЕНТР</p><p>ЗАГРУЗКИ</p><p>ФАЙЛОВ</p><p>|</p><p>ЦИФРОВОЙ</p><p>ТРАНСФЕР</p><p>|</p>
      <p>АКТИВЕН</p><p>|</p><p>100%</p><p>|</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
